From: SystoleOS <systole@example.org>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] COMP: Install vtkOpenGLResourceFreeCallback header

vtkOpenGLResourceFreeCallback.h is a public template utility used by
Slicer extensions (e.g. Slicer-Liver).  It was present in the source
tree but not listed in the cmake module's CLASSES, HEADERS, or
NOWRAP_HEADERS, so it was not installed as part of vtk_module_add_module.

Add it to NOWRAP_HEADERS (it is a template, so no Python wrapping is
possible or desired).
---
 Rendering/OpenGL2/CMakeLists.txt | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Rendering/OpenGL2/CMakeLists.txt b/Rendering/OpenGL2/CMakeLists.txt
index 1234567..abcdef0 100644
--- a/Rendering/OpenGL2/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/Rendering/OpenGL2/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -103,6 +103,7 @@ set(headers

 set(nowrap_headers
   vtkCompositeMapperHelper2.h
+  vtkOpenGLResourceFreeCallback.h
 )

 # add opengl support test executable on windows
